long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI Drive right next to your ChatGPT window! Use AI with any PDF on the web. Fact-check ChatGPT answers with your source documents and simplify the copy-and-paste of file links between AI Drive and ChatGPT. AI Drive allows you to edit and save your GPT chats as PDFs and also save PDFs to AI Drive with one click.
